import {Avatar, Box, Flex, HStack, Icon, IconButton, Text,} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import {RiMenuLine, RiNotificationLine,} from "react-icons/ri"

const Header = () => (
  <Flex w="100%" as="header" h="20">
    <Flex align="center">
      <IconButton icon={<RiMenuLine/>} fontSize="20"/>
    </Flex>
    <Flex align="center" ml="auto">
      <HStack
        mx="8"
        pr="8"
        py="1"
        spacing="8"
        color="gray.300"
        borderRightWidth={1}
        borderColor="gray.700"
      >
        <Icon as={RiNotificationLine} fontSize="20"/>
      </HStack>
      <Flex align="center" mr="4">
        <Box mr="4" textAlign="right">
          <Text>Victor Mesquita</Text>
          <Text color="gray.300" fontSize="small">
            mesquitadev@gmail.com
          </Text>
        </Box>
        <Avatar size="md" name="Victor Mesquita"/>
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  </Flex>
)

export default Header
